IndicatorDesc: Dollar value of financial and technical assistance (including through North-South, South-South and triangular cooperation) committed to developing countries
SeriesDesc: Total official development assistance (gross disbursement) for technical cooperation (millions of 2016 United States dollars)
Source: Creditor Reporting System (CRS) database, 2018, The Organisation for Economic Co-operation and Development (OECD)
Footnotes: [2000-2001]: Commitments; Based on OECD, CRS databased, 2018; Constant 2016 USD million // [2002-2016]: Gross disbursements; Based on OECD, CRS databased, 2018; Constant 2016 USD million
